1
00:00:27,525 --> 00:00:29,719
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:29,720 --> 00:00:33,661
=Episode 11=
(You were like a light I stumbled upon,)

3
00:00:33,662 --> 00:00:36,957
(shining into my chaotic life.)

4
00:00:47,500 --> 00:00:48,499
(100 years ago)

5
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:49,339
Lady He,

6
00:00:49,340 --> 00:00:50,900
you're heading out
for free clinic again?

7
00:00:51,180 --> 00:00:53,099
Lady He, come over for a meal sometime.

8
00:00:53,100 --> 00:00:53,579
Sure.

9
00:00:53,580 --> 00:00:54,499
Hello, Lady He.

10
00:00:54,500 --> 00:00:55,339
Hello.

11
00:00:55,340 --> 00:00:56,179
Lady He,

12
00:00:56,180 --> 00:00:57,299
we made cured meat at home.

13
00:00:57,300 --> 00:00:58,660
I'll bring you some in a few days.

14
00:01:28,350 --> 00:01:29,670
Hey, cutie.

15
00:01:29,940 --> 00:01:31,380
(Baihua Hall)
I finally found you.

16
00:01:39,500 --> 00:01:41,000
(Demon Heart's Consciousness)
Hello?

17
00:01:42,060 --> 00:01:43,300
Anyone here?

18
00:01:43,620 --> 00:01:46,020
No one's here.

19
00:01:50,780 --> 00:01:52,940
You're really cute.

20
00:01:55,340 --> 00:01:56,380
Who...

21
00:01:56,540 --> 00:01:57,820
Who are you?

22
00:01:58,060 --> 00:02:01,460
(Demon Heart, Hua Hui)
You may call me Hua Hui.

23
00:02:01,620 --> 00:02:02,860
From now on,

24
00:02:03,340 --> 00:02:05,220
you and I are one.

25
00:02:05,420 --> 00:02:06,940
You are officially

26
00:02:07,340 --> 00:02:09,580
a demon now.

27
00:02:11,420 --> 00:02:13,940
How could I have such a strange dream?

28
00:02:16,620 --> 00:02:18,220
Wake up.

29
00:02:18,380 --> 00:02:19,420
Wake up.

30
00:02:19,900 --> 00:02:21,139
My lady!

31
00:02:21,140 --> 00:02:23,540
If you die, what will we...

32
00:02:24,700 --> 00:02:26,980
(Attendant of Baihua Hall, Bai)
There's a ghost!

33
00:02:28,700 --> 00:02:30,899
I merely fell asleep.

34
00:02:30,900 --> 00:02:32,699
(Physician of Baihua Hall, He Yi)

35
00:02:32,700 --> 00:02:34,139
Don't curse me like that.

36
00:02:34,140 --> 00:02:34,899
Just now,

37
00:02:34,900 --> 00:02:36,139
I couldn't feel your pulse.

38
00:02:36,140 --> 00:02:36,779
Village chief!

39
00:02:36,780 --> 00:02:38,259
Bring me to have a look.

40
00:02:38,260 --> 00:02:39,619
Hurry, Chief Zhang.

41
00:02:39,620 --> 00:02:41,460
My lady is dead.

42
00:02:42,540 --> 00:02:43,699
My lady!

43
00:02:43,700 --> 00:02:44,820
My lady!

44
00:02:46,300 --> 00:02:48,020
(Attendant of Baihua hall, Hua)
Oh you.

45
00:02:48,100 --> 00:02:49,420
Hua.

46
00:02:50,260 --> 00:02:51,300
Chief Zhang.

47
00:02:51,740 --> 00:02:52,659
It's all my fault.

48
00:02:52,660 --> 00:02:54,539
I didn't discipline them well.

49
00:02:54,540 --> 00:02:56,699
(Village Chief, Zhang Muzhi)
Xi, you don't know yet,

50
00:02:56,700 --> 00:02:57,739
but that butcher Zhang

51
00:02:57,740 --> 00:02:59,259
heard you died

52
00:02:59,260 --> 00:03:00,819
and is on his way

53
00:03:00,820 --> 00:03:02,419
to seize your Baihua Hall.

54
00:03:02,420 --> 00:03:03,540
What?

55
00:03:04,260 --> 00:03:05,420
How dare he?

56
00:03:05,660 --> 00:03:08,020
No one's taking the Baihua Hall
my master left me.

57
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:09,859
He's a murderer

58
00:03:09,860 --> 00:03:11,259
hiding in our village.

59
00:03:11,260 --> 00:03:11,859
How about this?

60
00:03:11,860 --> 00:03:13,419
Take the two of them and leave.

61
00:03:13,420 --> 00:03:14,740
I'll hold them off.

62
00:03:15,700 --> 00:03:17,019
Who's the murderer?

63
00:03:17,020 --> 00:03:18,900
Who are you calling a murderer?

64
00:03:22,540 --> 00:03:23,579
Let's talk this out!

65
00:03:23,580 --> 00:03:24,659
Carrying weapons like this

66
00:03:24,660 --> 00:03:26,540
is beneath civility.

67
00:03:28,580 --> 00:03:29,659
He Xi,

68
00:03:29,660 --> 00:03:32,219
move out willingly today,

69
00:03:32,220 --> 00:03:33,539
and I'll spare your life.

70
00:03:33,540 --> 00:03:34,659
If not,

71
00:03:34,660 --> 00:03:37,180
I'll make the news
of your death come true.

72
00:03:37,700 --> 00:03:38,860
This is my hall.

73
00:03:39,140 --> 00:03:40,699
Anyone can come in,

74
00:03:40,700 --> 00:03:42,740
but not scum like you.

75
00:03:43,980 --> 00:03:45,060
Guys,

76
00:03:45,100 --> 00:03:46,180
get them.

77
00:03:46,980 --> 00:03:47,739
You guys!

78
00:03:47,740 --> 00:03:48,699
Don't push it.

79
00:03:48,700 --> 00:03:49,539
Come any closer

80
00:03:49,540 --> 00:03:50,580
and I'll...

81
00:03:51,420 --> 00:03:52,859
I'll report you!

82
00:03:52,860 --> 00:03:54,579
Don't forget

83
00:03:54,580 --> 00:03:56,699
who lent you money

84
00:03:56,700 --> 00:03:58,859
for your business.

85
00:03:58,860 --> 00:04:00,419
Debt is debt.

86
00:04:00,420 --> 00:04:01,979
but protecting her

87
00:04:01,980 --> 00:04:03,140
is another matter.

88
00:04:04,100 --> 00:04:05,460
Go to hell.

89
00:04:05,580 --> 00:04:06,699
Get lost

90
00:04:06,700 --> 00:04:07,819
or I'll kill you!

91
00:04:07,820 --> 00:04:09,219
(I need to get help.)

92
00:04:09,220 --> 00:04:10,539
(I can't save her alone.)

93
00:04:10,540 --> 00:04:12,620
(I need to get somebody.)

94
00:04:13,700 --> 00:04:14,539
Kill her.

95
00:04:14,540 --> 00:04:16,340
Then sell the kid in the city.

96
00:04:17,450 --> 00:04:18,307
Go to hell.

97
00:04:18,660 --> 00:04:19,740
Cutie,

98
00:04:19,820 --> 00:04:20,980
let me help you.

99
00:04:24,300 --> 00:04:25,460
Humans

100
00:04:26,420 --> 00:04:28,180
are sometimes worse than demons.

101
00:04:29,580 --> 00:04:31,180
I like that.

102
00:04:36,740 --> 00:04:38,420
My lady!

103
00:04:44,740 --> 00:04:46,580
I'd need to treat her injuries

104
00:04:46,860 --> 00:04:48,457
or I won't survive either.

105
00:04:51,860 --> 00:04:53,259
Take this jade whistle

106
00:04:53,260 --> 00:04:54,779
and keep it safe.

107
00:04:54,780 --> 00:04:57,580
(Young He Yi)
It'll protect you when needed.

108
00:04:57,660 --> 00:04:58,780
(The whistle.)

109
00:04:59,100 --> 00:05:00,340
(My whistle.)

110
00:05:00,860 --> 00:05:02,660
My lady!

111
00:05:21,660 --> 00:05:23,019
Who's this pretty boy?

112
00:05:23,020 --> 00:05:25,420
How dare you ruin my plans?

113
00:05:25,660 --> 00:05:27,019
(God Ye Zhao)
If she can summon me,

114
00:05:27,020 --> 00:05:28,420
then we are fated.

115
00:05:28,660 --> 00:05:31,220
I will help her today.

116
00:05:33,340 --> 00:05:35,099
How dare you oppose me?

117
00:05:35,100 --> 00:05:36,420
You've got a death wish?

118
00:05:43,420 --> 00:05:44,420
Kill him!

119
00:06:02,700 --> 00:06:03,779
My lady,

120
00:06:03,780 --> 00:06:05,270
are you alright?

121
00:06:05,340 --> 00:06:07,580
You were badly hurt.

122
00:06:08,260 --> 00:06:09,740
Where's the wound?

123
00:06:12,020 --> 00:06:14,019
It's the man in white from that night.

124
00:06:14,020 --> 00:06:15,780
Could he be a god?

125
00:06:18,460 --> 00:06:19,659
Hua, Bai,

126
00:06:19,660 --> 00:06:21,900
come help him inside.

127
00:06:22,220 --> 00:06:24,859
My lady, are you treating him?

128
00:06:24,860 --> 00:06:27,339
We're dragging him in to be my husband.

129
00:06:27,340 --> 00:06:28,419
(Qingxin Pavilion)
You two,

130
00:06:28,420 --> 00:06:30,020
carry him inside.

131
00:06:33,660 --> 00:06:35,100
The two of you

132
00:06:35,660 --> 00:06:36,779
may leave first.

133
00:06:36,780 --> 00:06:38,220
Yes, my lady.

134
00:06:48,580 --> 00:06:50,899
(Take your hand off, Cutie.)

135
00:06:50,900 --> 00:06:52,820
Who's inside my body?

136
00:06:57,220 --> 00:06:59,219
Take your hand off.

137
00:06:59,220 --> 00:07:01,100
Are you Hua Hui?

138
00:07:01,900 --> 00:07:03,780
I saved your life.

139
00:07:04,020 --> 00:07:06,419
Now help me kill him.

140
00:07:06,420 --> 00:07:08,660
But he saved us today.

141
00:07:08,700 --> 00:07:10,632
How could I turn on someone
who helped me?

142
00:07:13,020 --> 00:07:15,780
Without me, you'd be dead.

143
00:07:19,660 --> 00:07:23,420
His immortal body
is weakened by heavenly backlash.

144
00:07:24,020 --> 00:07:26,660
This is my best chance to kill him.

145
00:07:27,340 --> 00:07:28,339
Let go.

146
00:07:28,340 --> 00:07:29,979
You saved me, yes,

147
00:07:29,980 --> 00:07:32,099
but didn't he save me too?

148
00:07:32,100 --> 00:07:34,111
I hid in your body

149
00:07:34,112 --> 00:07:36,152
to escape his pursuit.

150
00:07:36,340 --> 00:07:38,060
We now share one life.

151
00:07:38,460 --> 00:07:41,420
He'll eventually discover
you're a demon.

152
00:07:41,460 --> 00:07:42,979
If you don't kill him today,

153
00:07:42,980 --> 00:07:44,659
he'll kill you first.

154
00:07:44,660 --> 00:07:46,979
We'll deal with the future later.

155
00:07:46,980 --> 00:07:49,659
If I hadn't used most of my power

156
00:07:49,660 --> 00:07:51,420
to heal you just now,

157
00:07:51,900 --> 00:07:54,420
I'd have taken over your body already.

158
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:56,510
Thank you for healing me,

159
00:07:56,660 --> 00:07:57,579
but

160
00:07:57,580 --> 00:07:58,780
I won't do it.

161
00:07:58,900 --> 00:08:00,900
Once I recover,

162
00:08:01,540 --> 00:08:03,220
I'll kill you

163
00:08:04,700 --> 00:08:06,420
then kill him.

164
00:08:11,140 --> 00:08:13,100
(Get out of my head!)

165
00:08:16,700 --> 00:08:19,100
It was just a small effort.
No need to kneel.

166
00:08:20,100 --> 00:08:21,420
My head is...

167
00:08:21,460 --> 00:08:25,780
(Cutie, don't you dare say a word.)

168
00:08:29,020 --> 00:08:30,540
My head is sick.

169
00:08:30,660 --> 00:08:32,780
I was just stretching
with the help of the bed board.

170
00:08:36,020 --> 00:08:38,220
(A familiar scent.)

171
00:08:43,020 --> 00:08:45,420
Our business is done. Farewell.

172
00:08:47,860 --> 00:08:49,339
You're leaving already?

173
00:08:49,340 --> 00:08:50,339
Anything else?

174
00:08:50,340 --> 00:08:52,020
You haven't paid yet.

175
00:08:52,340 --> 00:08:54,019
Money is worldly.

176
00:08:54,020 --> 00:08:54,899
I have none.

177
00:08:54,900 --> 00:08:56,099
But

178
00:08:56,100 --> 00:08:58,219
I can grant you three wishes

179
00:08:58,220 --> 00:08:59,860
to repay you for saving me.

180
00:09:01,140 --> 00:09:02,300
Really?

181
00:09:02,340 --> 00:09:03,019
Really.

182
00:09:03,020 --> 00:09:04,459
(Ask him to kill himself.)

183
00:09:04,460 --> 00:09:05,899
(Ask him to kill himself.)

184
00:09:05,900 --> 00:09:07,220
(Ask him to kill himself.)

185
00:09:09,460 --> 00:09:10,579
My...

186
00:09:10,580 --> 00:09:11,900
My first wish is...

187
00:09:14,100 --> 00:09:16,219
I want to know your name

188
00:09:16,220 --> 00:09:17,380
and if you're married.

189
00:09:20,100 --> 00:09:21,420
That's two wishes.

190
00:09:23,100 --> 00:09:24,540
This wish

191
00:09:24,740 --> 00:09:26,140
doesn't seem

192
00:09:26,460 --> 00:09:28,979
to matter much to you.

193
00:09:28,980 --> 00:09:30,219
To me,

194
00:09:30,220 --> 00:09:31,420
it does.

195
00:09:35,580 --> 00:09:36,780
My name is Ye Zhao,

196
00:09:36,860 --> 00:09:38,300
and I've never been married.

197
00:09:38,460 --> 00:09:39,780
Ye Zhao?

198
00:09:41,700 --> 00:09:44,379
So even gods have names.

199
00:09:44,380 --> 00:09:45,859
Then I'll call you Zhao.

200
00:09:45,860 --> 00:09:47,339
I'm He Xi,

201
00:09:47,340 --> 00:09:48,900
the physican of Baihua Hall.

202
00:09:49,380 --> 00:09:52,180
You can call me Xi.

203
00:09:53,340 --> 00:09:54,624
You have one wish left.

204
00:09:54,625 --> 00:09:55,705
I haven't decided yet.

205
00:09:57,980 --> 00:09:59,900
Then tell me after you've decided.

206
00:10:00,180 --> 00:10:01,619
You're leaving already?

207
00:10:01,620 --> 00:10:03,619
How will I find you?

208
00:10:03,620 --> 00:10:04,780
Ye Zhao!

209
00:10:06,700 --> 00:10:08,900
Gods really are heartless.

210
00:10:17,060 --> 00:10:18,979
(Since you've found the demon heart,)

211
00:10:18,980 --> 00:10:20,420
(why didn't you destroy it?)

212
00:10:20,580 --> 00:10:22,300
(She saves lives.)

213
00:10:22,340 --> 00:10:23,540
(Why destroy it?)

214
00:10:26,425 --> 00:10:27,579
Ten coins for consultation,

215
00:10:27,580 --> 00:10:28,700
and ten coins for the meds.

216
00:10:30,300 --> 00:10:31,579
When have I ever charged?

217
00:10:31,580 --> 00:10:32,540
Go get the medicine.

218
00:10:33,620 --> 00:10:35,180
Thank you, Lady He.

219
00:10:35,860 --> 00:10:37,180
Lady He,

220
00:10:37,340 --> 00:10:39,339
my mother asked me to give you this

221
00:10:39,340 --> 00:10:41,380
to thank you for saving her.

222
00:10:42,180 --> 00:10:44,939
(She may appear kind today,)

223
00:10:44,940 --> 00:10:47,099
(but tomorrow
she may reveal her true form)

224
00:10:47,100 --> 00:10:48,619
(and harm others.)

225
00:10:48,620 --> 00:10:50,420
(Let's worry about that in the future.)

226
00:10:50,575 --> 00:10:53,095
(I'll kill her before she harms others.)

227
00:10:53,100 --> 00:10:54,474
(She is kind today,)

228
00:10:54,475 --> 00:10:55,835
(so I won't kill her.)

229
00:10:56,820 --> 00:10:57,939
My lady,

230
00:10:57,940 --> 00:10:59,379
don't be sad.

231
00:10:59,380 --> 00:11:01,960
Since he's gone, just let him go.

232
00:11:02,280 --> 00:11:04,040
If you don't know what to say,
just don't talk.

233
00:11:04,100 --> 00:11:05,739
My lady, don't be sad.

234
00:11:05,740 --> 00:11:06,739
Just let him go.

235
00:11:06,740 --> 00:11:08,859
Hua and I will stay with you forever

236
00:11:08,860 --> 00:11:10,180
and take care of you till the end.

237
00:11:11,620 --> 00:11:12,700
You two,

238
00:11:13,500 --> 00:11:15,420
go to sleep.

239
00:11:15,860 --> 00:11:18,540
Alright, let's go.

240
00:11:21,980 --> 00:11:23,180
What's going on?

241
00:11:29,500 --> 00:11:30,940
Could it be

242
00:11:31,740 --> 00:11:33,940
love at first sight?

243
00:11:34,860 --> 00:11:36,219
No, no, no!

244
00:11:36,220 --> 00:11:37,660
Impossible.

245
00:11:42,837 --> 00:11:45,917
(This whistle never worked before,)

246
00:11:46,100 --> 00:11:47,620
(but the moment I blew it,)

247
00:11:47,860 --> 00:11:49,780
(he came.)

248
00:11:59,100 --> 00:12:00,580
(What if I try again?)

249
00:12:15,575 --> 00:12:17,284
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

250
00:12:17,285 --> 00:12:20,134
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

251
00:12:20,135 --> 00:12:22,874
♪I'd rather this night never end♪

252
00:12:22,875 --> 00:12:24,504
♪Let the long shadows♪

253
00:12:24,505 --> 00:12:30,105
♪whisper what's in your heart♪

254
00:12:30,155 --> 00:12:31,754
♪If in a dream♪

255
00:12:31,755 --> 00:12:34,514
♪I can hear your voice♪

256
00:12:34,515 --> 00:12:37,364
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

257
00:12:37,365 --> 00:12:39,964
♪Let it be us♪

258
00:12:39,965 --> 00:12:44,754
♪drawing endlessly close♪

259
00:12:44,755 --> 00:12:46,514
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

260
00:12:46,515 --> 00:12:49,165
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

261
00:12:49,385 --> 00:12:52,104
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

262
00:12:52,105 --> 00:12:53,754
♪Not even in time♪

263
00:12:53,755 --> 00:12:59,414
♪to tell you how I feel♪

264
00:12:59,415 --> 00:13:00,954
♪If the rain won't stop♪

265
00:13:00,955 --> 00:13:03,704
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

266
00:13:03,705 --> 00:13:06,674
♪Let love go on♪

267
00:13:06,675 --> 00:13:09,224
♪Until forever♪

268
00:13:09,225 --> 00:13:13,864
♪Until we slowly grow old♪

269
00:13:13,865 --> 00:13:16,474
♪Until forever♪

270
00:13:16,475 --> 00:13:23,585
♪Until we slowly grow old♪
